<!--#include virtual="/header_end.inc"-->

<font size=5>W</font>elcome to the Boise Center's alumni office.  We strive to be a convenient conduit for the transfer of ideas and resources between the University of Idaho and its alumni in the greater Boise area (about 10,000).  The associate director in Boise is <a href="/employee/detail.asp?email_name=nmcdan">Nancy McDaniel</a>.
